            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chowder is cooking, drain and rinse your<strong> butter beans</strong> and wash your <strong>shredded kale </strong>then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once the potatoes are tender, add your<strong> soft cheese</strong>, <strong>kale</strong> and <strong>drained butter beans </strong>to the<strong> </strong>chorizo chowder, stir it all together and cover with a lid</p><p>Cook for a further 5 min or until the kale is wilted and the butter beans are warmed through</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
